FROM [Works] AS [w]
INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c] ON [w].[CustomerId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Discriminator], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [a].[IsWorker]
    FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Discriminator] = N'User'
) AS [t] ON [c].[UserId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [UserInfos] AS [u] ON [t].[Id] = [u].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN [Employees] AS [e] ON [w].[WorkerId] = [e].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[AccessFailedCount], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a0].[Discriminator], [a0].[Email], [a0].[EmailConfirmed], [a0].[LockoutEnabled], [a0].[LockoutEnd], [a0].[NormalizedEmail], [a0].[NormalizedUserName], [a0].[PasswordHash], [a0].[PhoneNumber], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a0].[SecurityStamp], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a0].[UserName], [a0].[IsWorker]

    WHERE [a0].[Discriminator] = N'User'
) AS [t0] ON [e].[UserId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [UserInfos] AS [u0] ON [t0].[Id] = [u0].[UserId]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c0] ON [w].[CategoryId] = [c0].[Id]

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Discriminator], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [a].[IsWorker]

LEFT JOIN [UserInfos] AS [u] ON [t].[Id] = [u].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN [Employees] AS [e] ON [w].[WorkerId] = [e].[Id]

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Discriminator], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [a].[IsWorker]

) AS [t] ON [c].[UserId] = [t].[Id]

WHERE [c].[Id] = @__id_0

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Discriminator], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [a].[IsWorker]

) AS [t] ON [c].[UserId] = [t].[Id]

WHERE [c].[Id] = @__id_0
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id], [u].[Id], [r].[Id]"

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Discriminator], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [a].[IsWorker]
    FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[Discriminator] = N'User'
) AS [t] ON [c].[UserId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [UserInfos] AS [u] ON [t].[Id] = [u].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN [Reviews] AS [r] ON [c].[Id] = [r].[CustomerId]
LEFT JOIN [Works] AS [w] ON [c].[Id] = [w].[CustomerId]
WHERE [c].[Id] = @__id_0
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id], [u].[Id], [r].[Id]"

""SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[UserId], [t].[Id], [t].[AccessFailedCount], [t].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t].[Discriminator], [t].[Email], [t].[EmailConfirmed], [t].[LockoutEnabled], [t].[LockoutEnd], [t].[NormalizedEmail], [t].[NormalizedUserName], [t].[PasswordHash], [t].[PhoneNumber], [t].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [t].[SecurityStamp], [t].[TwoFactorEnabled], [t].[UserName], [t].[IsWorker], [u].[Id], [u].[Account], [u].[Information], [u].[Name], [u].[Phone], [u].[PhotoPath], [u].[Surname], [u].[UserId], [r].[Id], [r].[CreatedTime], [r].[CustomerId], [r].[Rating], [r].[Text], [r].[WorkerId], [w].[Id], [w].[CategoryId], [w].[Context], [w].[Created], [w].[CustomerId], [w].[Finish], [w].[IsFinished], [w].[IsPublicshed], [w].[Name], [w].[Price], [w].[TypeOfPayment], [w].[Validation], [w].[WorkerId]

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Discriminator], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [a].[IsWorker]

    WHERE [a].[Discriminator] = N'User'
) AS [t] ON [c].[UserId] = [t].[Id]

WHERE [c].[Id] = @__id_0
ORDER BY [c].[Id], [t].[Id], [u].[Id], [r].[Id]"

) AS [t] ON [e].[UserId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [UserInfos] AS [u] ON [t].[Id] = [u].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[Id], [w].[CategoryId], [w].[Context], [w].[Created], [w].[CustomerId], [w].[Finish], [w].[IsFinished], [w].[IsPublicshed], [w].[Name], [w].[Price], [w].[TypeOfPayment], [w].[Validation], [w].[WorkerId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[UserId]

) AS [t0] ON [e].[Id] = [t0].[WorkerId]
LEFT JOIN (

        WHERE [a0].[Discriminator] = N'User'
    ) AS [t2] ON [c0].[UserId] = [t2].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [UserInfos] AS [u0] ON [t2].[Id] = [u0].[UserId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[Id] = [t1].[WorkerId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].[EmployeesId], [e0].[SkillsID], [s].[ID], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Name]
    FROM [EmployeeSkill] AS [e0]
    INNER JOIN [Skill] AS [s] ON [e0].[SkillsID] = [s].[ID]
) AS [t3] ON [e].[Id] = [t3].[EmployeesId]
WHERE [e].[Id] = @__employeeId_0
ORDER BY [e].[Id], [t].[Id], [u].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id1], [t1].[Id2], [t3].[EmployeesId], [t3].[SkillsID]"

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Discriminator], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [a].[IsWorker]

    WHERE [a].[Discriminator] = N'User'
) AS [t] ON [e].[UserId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [UserInfos] AS [u] ON [t].[Id] = [u].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[Id], [w].[CategoryId], [w].[Context], [w].[Created], [w].[CustomerId], [w].[Finish], [w].[IsFinished], [w].[IsPublicshed], [w].[Name], [w].[Price], [w].[TypeOfPayment], [w].[Validation], [w].[WorkerId], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[UserId]
    FROM [Works] AS [w]
    INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c] ON [w].[CustomerId] = [c].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [e].[Id] = [t0].[WorkerId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [r].[Id], [r].[CreatedTime], [r].[CustomerId], [r].[Rating], [r].[Text], [r].[WorkerId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[UserId], [t2].[Id] AS [Id1], [t2].[AccessFailedCount], [t2].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t2].[Discriminator], [t2].[Email], [t2].[EmailConfirmed], [t2].[LockoutEnabled], [t2].[LockoutEnd], [t2].[NormalizedEmail], [t2].[NormalizedUserName], [t2].[PasswordHash], [t2].[PhoneNumber], [t2].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [t2].[SecurityStamp], [t2].[TwoFactorEnabled], [t2].[UserName], [t2].[IsWorker], [u0].[Id] AS [Id2], [u0].[Account], [u0].[Information], [u0].[Name], [u0].[Phone], [u0].[PhotoPath], [u0].[Surname], [u0].[UserId] AS [UserId0]

    INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c0] ON [r].[CustomerId] = [c0].[Id]

        SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[AccessFailedCount], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a0].[Discriminator], [a0].[Email], [a0].[EmailConfirmed], [a0].[LockoutEnabled], [a0].[LockoutEnd], [a0].[NormalizedEmail], [a0].[NormalizedUserName], [a0].[PasswordHash], [a0].[PhoneNumber], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a0].[SecurityStamp], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a0].[UserName], [a0].[IsWorker]
        FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [a0]
        WHERE [a0].[Discriminator] = N'User'
    ) AS [t2] ON [c0].[UserId] = [t2].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [UserInfos] AS [u0] ON [t2].[Id] = [u0].[UserId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[Id] = [t1].[WorkerId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].[EmployeesId], [e0].[SkillsID], [s].[ID], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Name]
    FROM [EmployeeSkill] AS [e0]
    INNER JOIN [Skill] AS [s] ON [e0].[SkillsID] = [s].[ID]
) AS [t3] ON [e].[Id] = [t3].[EmployeesId]
WHERE [e].[Id] = @__employeeId_0
ORDER BY [e].[Id], [t].[Id], [u].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id1], [t1].[Id2], [t3].[EmployeesId], [t3].[SkillsID]"

    INNER JOIN [Customers] AS [c0] ON [r].[CustomerId] = [c0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[AccessFailedCount], [a0].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a0].[Discriminator], [a0].[Email], [a0].[EmailConfirmed], [a0].[LockoutEnabled], [a0].[LockoutEnd], [a0].[NormalizedEmail], [a0].[NormalizedUserName], [a0].[PasswordHash], [a0].[PhoneNumber], [a0].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a0].[SecurityStamp], [a0].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a0].[UserName], [a0].[IsWorker]
        FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [a0]
        WHERE [a0].[Discriminator] = N'User'
    ) AS [t2] ON [c0].[UserId] = [t2].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [UserInfos] AS [u0] ON [t2].[Id] = [u0].[UserId]
) AS [t1] ON [e].[Id] = [t1].[WorkerId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].[EmployeesId], [e0].[SkillsID], [s].[ID], [s].[CategoryId], [s].[Name]
    FROM [EmployeeSkill] AS [e0]
    INNER JOIN [Skill] AS [s] ON [e0].[SkillsID] = [s].[ID]
) AS [t3] ON [e].[Id] = [t3].[EmployeesId]
WHERE [e].[Id] = @__employeeId_0
ORDER BY [e].[Id], [t].[Id], [u].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id1], [t1].[Id2], [t3].[EmployeesId], [t3].[SkillsID]"

LEFT JOIN [Customers] AS [c] ON [a].[Id] = [c].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN [Employees] AS [e] ON [a].[Id] = [e].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN [UserInfos] AS [u] ON [a].[Id] = [u].[UserId]
